## Adding New Components

When you need a new UI component:

1. Check if shadcn has it: https://ui.shadcn.com/docs/components
2. Add it using: `npx shadcn@latest add [component-name]`
3. Use it from `@/components/ui/[component-name]`

## Component Variants

Use shadcn's variant system with `cva`:

```typescript
const buttonVariants = cva(
  "base-classes",
  {
    variants: {
      variant: { default: "...", destructive: "..." },
      size: { default: "...", sm: "...", lg: "..." }
    }
  }
);
```

See `src/components/ui/button.tsx` for a complete example.